<h2>Install</h2>

<pre>
  ember install ember-cli-pagedown
  bower install --save https://github.com/ujifgc/pagedown.git#f1ae0f5626e044f64b937836962a9941c60c7596 

  # if ember-cli &lt;= 0.2.2
  ember install:addon ember-cli-pagedown
  bower install --save https://github.com/ujifgc/pagedown.git#f1ae0f5626e044f64b937836962a9941c60c7596 
</pre>

